			<div class="entry-utility">
									<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/category/fresh-ideas/" rel="category tag">Fresh Ideas</a>					</span>
								
	<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
	<span class="tag-links">
		<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/caterpillars/" rel="tag">caterpillars</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/entrepreneur/" rel="tag">entrepreneur</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/fresh-idea/" rel="tag">fresh idea</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/invention/" rel="tag">invention</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/organic/" rel="tag">organic</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/pests/" rel="tag">pests</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/simple-living/" rel="tag">Simple Living</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/slugs/" rel="tag">slugs</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/whidbey/" rel="tag">Whidbey</a>	</span>

