			<div class="entry-utility">
									<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a>					</span>
								
	<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
	<span class="tag-links">
		<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/airbnb/" rel="tag">AirBnB</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/banks/" rel="tag">banks</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/berkshares/" rel="tag">BerkShares</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/bitcoin/" rel="tag">bitcoin</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/cryptocurrency/" rel="tag">cryptocurrency</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/economy/" rel="tag">economy</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/finance/" rel="tag">finance</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/investing/" rel="tag">investing</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/kiva/" rel="tag">Kiva</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/lendingclub/" rel="tag">LendingClub</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/lyft/" rel="tag">Lyft</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/mazacoin/" rel="tag">MazaCoin</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/microloans/" rel="tag">microloans</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/occupy/" rel="tag">occupy</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/peer-lending/" rel="tag">peer lending</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/peer-to-peer/" rel="tag">peer-to-peer</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/personal-finance/" rel="tag">personal finance</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/sharing-economy/" rel="tag">sharing economy</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/stocks/" rel="tag">stocks</a>, <a href="http://trimbathcreative.wordpress.com/tag/wall-street/" rel="tag">Wall Street</a>	</span>

